<HEAD><TITLE>

Free Speech Trumps Clinton Wiretap Plan

</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffFF">


<!-- Header/Nav-Bar Table -------------------------------------------->

