<HEAD><TITLE>

GERMAN GOVERNMENT PUSHES BLOCKAGE OF NETHERLANDS WEB SITES.
</TITLE>
<META NAME="description" CONTENT="The Global Clearinghouse for Information Warfare on the Internet">
<META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="
