<center><h2>


</h2>
<B>
Date:       Mon, 19 Aug 96 15:03:12 EST<BR>
Dr Michael Baker, EFA Board Member, PO Box 5, Flaxley SA 5153, Australia<BR>
</h3>
Ph:08 388 8439 Fax:08 262 3633 08=+618 mbaker@pobox.com http://pobox.com/~mbaker<BR>
Internet censorship won't protect Children, but it will destroy their future<BR>
<a href="http://www.efa.org.au">Join the STOP! Campaign</a> or 
<A HREF="MAILTO:campaign@efa.org.au">campaign@efa.org.au</a><BR>
