<HEAD><TITLE>

Clinton's CyberWar Executive Order

</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffFF">


<!-- Header/Nav-Bar Table -------------------------------------------->

<table width=580 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
