<H4>10/26/96</H4>

 <LI>  URL for the  homepage of the U.S. Arms Control and Disarmament
Agency at <a href="http://www.acda.gov">http://www.acda.gov</a> Information on several important treaties is
posted here, including START I, START II, CFE, etc.<BR>
   ACDA also publishes the annual _World Military Expenditures and Arms
Transfers_ report, a useful document for information on military spending,
imports, exports, etc. This document and others are available at the home
page as well.<BR>
