<P>Don't miss it!

<P><CENTER>     ----------------------------------------------------------------</CENTER>


<P>Have you ever hacked a machine in your hometown from a foreign
country?

<P>Have you ever had to convert dollars into pesos to get your bribe right?

<P>Have you ever spent time in a foreign prison, where your "rights as an 
American" just don't apply?

<P>Have you ever been taken down for soemthing that wasn't even illegal 
half an hour ago?

<P>YOU WILL!  And the con that will bring it to you?

