<HEAD><TITLE>
SOURCES eJOURNAL announces SOURCES BRIEFINGS

</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffFF">


<!-- Header/Nav-Bar Table -------------------------------------------->

<table width=580 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
<tr>
<td valign=top width=48>
<a href="http://www.infowar.com/resource/resource.html-ssi"><img width=48 height=68 border=0 src="../../images/back.gif" alt="Back"></a>
</td>
<td valign=top width=48>
