<HEAD><TITLE>

International Symposium on Technology and Society 1997 (ISTAS'97)
</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffFF">


<!-- Header/Nav-Bar Table -------------------------------------------->

<table width=580 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
<tr>
<td valign=top width=48>
