KillerApp Communications Julie Gladders/John Murphy<BR>
213/938-7600/212/727-1030 <BR>
<a href="MAILTO:jgladders@kappcomm.com">jgladders@kappcomm.com</a> <BR>
<a href="MAILTO:jmurphy@kappcomm.com">jmurphy@kappcomm.com</a> or<BR>
Ernst & Young LLP Keith Hark 212/773-5299 <BR>
<a href="MAILTO:keith.hark@ey.com">keith.hark@ey.com</a> <BR>
UNITED STATES <BR>
BUSINESS WIRE 21/10/96 <BR>

